You can obtain rewards through the following methods:
· Consume 20 Original Resin to receive the normal amount of rewards;
· Consume 40 Original Resin to receive rewards equivalent to <color=#FFCC33>2 completions</color> of the challenge;
· Consume 1 Condensed Resin, Transient Resin, or Fragile Resin to receive rewards equivalent to <color=#FFCC33>3 completions</color> of the challenge. When multiple types of resin are available, they will be consumed in the following order: Condensed Resin, Transient Resin, Fragile Resin.
· Consume Primogems to receive rewards equivalent to <color=#FFCC33>3 completions</color> of the challenge. Using Primogems to claim rewards shares the same daily usage count and limit as restoring Original Resin with Primogems, and the more times this method is used in a single day, the higher the Primogem cost.
Additionally, when you consume Transient Resin, Fragile Resin, or Primogems to claim rewards, <color=#FFCC33>it will count as consuming 60 Original Resin, which will grant progress towards tasks in your Journal that require you to consume Original Resin, and thus convert Long-Term Encounter Points into Encounter Points</color>.
